00:00:10.240 --> 00:00:18.320
Please come and sit down.

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:20.880
For those people who’ve come
for the first time,

00:00:20.880 --> 00:00:24.720
let me introduce to you
Mataji Nirmala Devi.

00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:28.240
She just arrived back from London
after a very brief return visit

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:35.200
where she had to accompany her husband
who’s a distinguished member

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:36.640
of the diplomatic community.

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:41.120
He’s Secretary General
of the United Nations Agency

00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:47.280
of the Maritime Agency

00:00:47.280 --> 00:00:50.880
and she’s come back to us
here in America.

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:57.760
Many of you have been before
and experienced Sahaja Yoga

00:00:57.760 --> 00:01:01.680
which means spontaneous union.

00:01:01.680 --> 00:01:06.160
And this is what makes Mataji
and Sahaja Yoga different

00:01:06.160 --> 00:01:13.680
to all the other searchings and pathways
that we’ve probably all been following

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:15.680
because it’s an actual happening.

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:19.040
It’s something that happens
in her presence,

00:01:19.040 --> 00:01:23.360
in the presence of a holy person,
a realised soul.

00:01:23.360 --> 00:01:27.075
The awakening occurs spontaneously.

00:01:27.075 --> 00:01:27.120
The awakening is the presence
of the Holy One.

00:01:27.120 --> 00:01:30.560
It’s not the promise
of something to come,

00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:37.040
it’s not striving, it’s not discipline,
it’s not certain practices

00:01:37.040 --> 00:01:40.480
which lead to the conclusion
of Self-realisation

00:01:40.480 --> 00:01:42.560
but it’s an actualisation.

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:47.360
So Mataji has to be
somebody very special.

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:50.240
But that you’ll find out yourself.

00:01:50.240 --> 00:01:52.720
When you get your realisation
you become connected

00:01:52.720 --> 00:01:57.040
to the all-pervading power of God

00:01:57.040 --> 00:02:00.880
and with that connection
you can find out the truth for yourself.

00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:08.560
You actually become like a computer
having been programmed this lifetime

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:11.680
and previous lives
right up to this point

00:02:11.680 --> 00:02:15.280
where as seekers you want the ultimate.

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:21.680
Now by her grace you get the connection
and when you get the connection

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:24.480
you get the ultimate.

00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:29.440
You find within your body
there is a subtle body

00:02:29.440 --> 00:02:34.800
which is the mechanism
which connects you.

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:39.520
That subtle body is the chakra system.

00:02:39.520 --> 00:02:46.560
In her presence the Kundalini rises
just as quickly as a split of a second

00:02:46.560 --> 00:02:48.160
in most cases.

00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:51.680
In people who damage their chakras
it may take a little longer

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:54.800
and may take some perseverance
on your part

00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:59.440
and a lot of care and nurturing
and a lot of love and compassion

00:02:59.440 --> 00:03:01.200
from our holy Mother.

00:03:01.200 --> 00:03:07.280
But Kundalini rises through the centres
and passes through the top of the head

00:03:07.280 --> 00:03:12.000
at this centre called the Brahma Andhra

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:16.880
and when that happens
you become your spirit.

00:03:16.880 --> 00:03:20.080
You become a Self-realised soul.

00:03:20.080 --> 00:03:26.080
You touch reality for the first time
in all your lives

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:28.960
that this actually happens.

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:31.760
Many people here tonight
have already got it

00:03:31.760 --> 00:03:33.840
because you see her presence is everywhere

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:37.840
and at the programs that we had
the last two nights

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:41.680
many people actually got the experience.

00:03:41.680 --> 00:03:44.480
As we said to you, Mother is everywhere.

00:03:44.480 --> 00:03:46.080
Her presence is everywhere

00:03:46.640 --> 00:03:51.120
and when you ask for it
with a humble heart,

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:57.600
when you ask for your Self-realisation
and your desire is a pure desire

00:03:57.600 --> 00:04:00.800
to be one with God, it’s granted.

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:04.720
The grace of God is overflowing
at this time.

00:04:04.720 --> 00:04:09.360
Mother often says that
on the tree of life

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:12.240
there were very few flowers at first.

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:18.000
Now there are many, many flowers
and the blossom time has come.

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:21.920
Many, many of those flowers
have to turn to fruit.

00:04:21.920 --> 00:04:24.720
And so you have to see
that this is what it is.

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:31.520
So without any further talking again
I’d like to introduce to you our Mother,

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:34.240
Mataji Nirmala Devi.

