and people will just see some bubbles
on the shores talking of big things.

00:13:31.600 --> 00:13:38.400
It is we who have to save ourselves first,
we have to build up ourselves first,

00:13:38.400 --> 00:13:43.520
we have to become ourselves inside
so that we become strong,

00:13:43.520 --> 00:13:46.640
so that we know we become the masters.

00:13:46.640 --> 00:13:54.000
It is not the mastery of the world,
but the mastery of your Self,

00:13:54.000 --> 00:13:57.600
which you should have.

