His kingdom is very different.

00:16:28.400 --> 00:16:34.080
He has got communications,
which are very subtle.

00:16:34.080 --> 00:16:38.880
His ways and methods are so great
that unless and until you come

00:16:38.880 --> 00:16:44.560
into His domain you won’t understand
how great He is.

