because it has manifested the whole,
the whole universe and everything,

00:20:03.040 --> 00:20:07.840
and still it has not manifested itself
because it is the residual power

00:20:07.840 --> 00:20:13.280
of your desire to be one with the Divine.

00:20:13.280 --> 00:20:17.040
Unless and until that has happened,
unless and until you are baptized –

00:20:17.040 --> 00:20:20.160
in the real sense,
the way John the Baptist did,

00:20:20.160 --> 00:20:24.080
not just somebody coming:
“Alright, I baptize you”.

00:20:24.080 --> 00:20:26.720
It’s all artificial, it’s all a drama.

00:20:26.720 --> 00:20:30.873
I’m Myself born a Christian,
I used to laugh aloud as a child,

00:20:30.873 --> 00:20:34.240
I used to laugh aloud: “What’s this
drama going on? No Kundalini rising,

00:20:34.240 --> 00:20:38.720
nothing, and they are baptizing!”.

00:20:38.720 --> 00:20:46.400
Baptism, John the Baptist could do,
because he was a realized soul.

00:20:46.400 --> 00:20:49.680
Those who are not realized
cannot give realization,

00:20:49.680 --> 00:20:52.320
they have no authority.

00:20:54.960 --> 00:21:00.480
Alright, even say, in ignorance
you believe that you can do it.

00:21:00.480 --> 00:21:05.200
But now, when it has come to reality,
must you not accept it?

00:21:05.200 --> 00:21:07.440
Must you not get it?

00:21:07.440 --> 00:21:12.400
Why this obstinacy not to get it,
I can’t understand.

00:21:12.400 --> 00:21:15.840
And this is what is wrong
with our rationality,

00:21:15.840 --> 00:21:21.280
that we can justify everything
that we know, like: “I believe”.

00:21:21.280 --> 00:21:25.200
Now if you believe that Kundalini is here,
what can I do about it?

00:21:25.200 --> 00:21:28.880
It is not, it is not, it is here.

00:21:28.880 --> 00:21:32.160
But because you have read a book
which was nine hundred pages,

00:21:32.160 --> 00:21:35.840
naturally you have paid so much effort,
you have every reason to believe

00:21:35.840 --> 00:21:39.600
in that book (She laughs) because you
have put it so much of effort

00:21:39.600 --> 00:21:42.480
that you can’t get over it:
“Now I’ve done Mother,

00:21:42.480 --> 00:21:45.440
what am I to do now? I believe in it”.

00:21:45.440 --> 00:21:49.040
Like the other day one fellow said –
there’s one anti-Christ, and he said:

00:21:49.040 --> 00:21:51.680
“I’m taking his name
for the last ten years,

00:21:51.680 --> 00:21:56.480
now how can I forget it?”.

00:21:56.480 --> 00:22:03.040
If you have lost something,
and you are searching it, and truly,

00:22:03.040 --> 00:22:08.880
even for ten years, and if you know that
that is not the way you find it,

00:22:08.880 --> 00:22:14.640
you will give up. Is common sense,
is absolute common sense one should have

00:22:14.640 --> 00:22:20.240
to understand that within us God must
have placed something beautifully

00:22:20.240 --> 00:22:22.640
to work it out and…

00:22:22.640 --> 00:22:26.320
The chakras and all that they have
started talking quite alright,

00:22:26.320 --> 00:22:29.520
some borrowed feathers from somewhere
I don’t know how;

00:22:29.520 --> 00:22:32.240
I don’t know if they know
about the chakras also besides see

00:22:32.240 --> 00:22:37.440
what they are like, how many centers
they have got, and how many they control,

00:22:37.440 --> 00:22:39.360
and they how they work out.

00:22:39.360 --> 00:22:43.280
I have no idea as to how much they know
and how much they have learnt,

00:22:43.280 --> 00:22:48.800
because you can read any book,
some tantrikas or somebody unauthorized

00:22:48.800 --> 00:22:51.760
might have told them something
and here comes the book.

00:22:51.760 --> 00:22:55.440
In America I think it is easiest
to publish any book.

00:22:55.440 --> 00:22:59.920
Nobody says no to anything that no sense,
so all kinds of books they may have wrote.

00:22:59.920 --> 00:23:03.840
And people are very fond of reading,
I was coming by plane and one gentleman

00:23:03.840 --> 00:23:06.000
finished three books, sitting next to Me.

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:12.000
I was amazed at his speed,
the way he was reading.

00:23:13.440 --> 00:23:25.120
This kind of reading gives us
a blurred idea, a confusion, about God.

00:23:25.120 --> 00:23:31.600
One has to know that if you become
the reality, you should be able to

00:23:31.600 --> 00:23:35.280
reason the reality, you should be able
to discriminate,

00:23:35.280 --> 00:23:37.920
you should be able to see reality.

00:23:37.920 --> 00:23:41.440
For example somebody says: “Oh, I am a
person who is born again,” or say

00:23:41.440 --> 00:23:43.280
“I am a realized soul”.

00:23:43.280 --> 00:23:48.160
Alright, if you are a realized soul,
can you tell Me what is the problem

00:23:48.160 --> 00:23:53.520
with this gentleman, can you tell me what
are the centers catching in this man,

00:23:53.520 --> 00:23:56.880
or can you tell Me what are your problems?

00:23:56.880 --> 00:23:59.920
At least minimum that much
you should know.

00:23:59.920 --> 00:24:01.920
They said: “No, no, that we don’t know,
but we are born again”.

00:24:01.920 --> 00:24:05.520
This is self-certification, I mean,
if you give a certificate to yourself –

00:24:05.520 --> 00:24:10.880
I am the President, President of America
– you don’t become.

00:24:10.880 --> 00:24:13.360
Like some people say: “I’m Omkara”

00:24:13.360 --> 00:24:17.040
By saying ‘I’m Omkara’, do you become?

00:24:17.040 --> 00:24:22.400
You have to really become.
Actually become.

00:24:22.400 --> 00:24:29.760
It has to happen within us,
that’s why becoming is the point.

00:24:29.760 --> 00:24:34.960
We should ask ourselves:
what did we become?

00:24:34.960 --> 00:24:36.400
Are we master of ourselves?

00:24:38.640 --> 00:24:45.040
Now one may say that,
‘What is the authority of Mataji?’.

00:24:45.040 --> 00:24:48.480
I have heard a thing like that (laughs).
It’s correct!

00:24:48.480 --> 00:24:52.400
I don’t say you should not
challenge the authority.

00:24:52.400 --> 00:24:59.760
But whose authority will you accept?
Best authority is yourself.

00:24:59.760 --> 00:25:05.120
If I say My authority is Christ,
if I say My authority is Rama,

00:25:05.120 --> 00:25:09.760
is Shri Krishna, and all the ancient
scriptures and all the scriptures,

00:25:09.760 --> 00:25:15.840
and all the great poets who have sung
the song of the truth are My authority,

00:25:15.840 --> 00:25:17.840
you won’t be able to relate.

00:25:17.840 --> 00:25:24.000
But the best thing is you yourself
should be the authority to judge Me.

00:25:24.000 --> 00:25:28.960
You yourself should know
and see for yourself.

00:25:28.960 --> 00:25:33.040
It’s like you bring ten people
in the room who are blind,

00:25:33.040 --> 00:25:40.800
there are no lights, and there you say
that the color of these flowers is red.

00:25:40.800 --> 00:25:46.400
Then you will say: “What is the
authority of yours that these are red?”.

00:25:46.400 --> 00:25:52.640
Now, because I can see! “But we cannot
see, so how are we to believe?”

00:25:52.640 --> 00:25:56.240
So best thing is that I open your eyes,
and put on the lights,

00:25:56.240 --> 00:25:59.040
and you see for yourself.

00:26:00.560 --> 00:26:02.800
You can also relatively see.

00:26:02.800 --> 00:26:06.960
For example a person who first time
has never seen a red color,

00:26:06.960 --> 00:26:11.480
or a blue or a black,
then how are you to tell him?

00:26:11.480 --> 00:26:16.080
You have to take something as an absolute,
you can say: “Alright, if this is red

00:26:16.080 --> 00:26:19.680
then that is red,
that is called as red”.

00:26:19.680 --> 00:26:23.360
In the same way we can relatively
also judge this.

00:26:23.360 --> 00:26:27.200
The other day I told you an example,
you take two people who are suffering

00:26:27.200 --> 00:26:33.440
from cancer, two people who are suffering
from say lunacy,

00:26:33.440 --> 00:26:36.400
and two people who are suffering
from fake gurus (laughter, laughs),

00:26:36.400 --> 00:26:42.960
and two people who are realized souls.
Or – and take two people

00:26:42.960 --> 00:26:46.240
who are not realized.
Let’s take like that, a group.

00:26:46.240 --> 00:26:51.600
Now, the person who is sitting before us
– you can see yourself, not Me –

00:26:51.600 --> 00:26:56.640
the one who is from lunatic asylum
or who has got problems, mental problems,

00:26:56.640 --> 00:26:59.120
will be shaking, like that.

00:26:59.120 --> 00:27:02.560
Some will shake little,
some will really rackle with it,

00:27:02.560 --> 00:27:04.960
absolutely rackle.

00:27:04.960 --> 00:27:09.360
Then, if you want to see the person
who has got cancer,

00:27:09.360 --> 00:27:15.120
he’ll be emitting heat so much, so much,
that the whole room will be filled

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:17.840
with hot air.

00:27:17.840 --> 00:27:22.880
Now, the third person, who is realized,
will feel cool breeze.

00:27:22.880 --> 00:27:26.320
Tremendous cool breeze, peace and bliss.

00:27:26.320 --> 00:27:30.320
And the one who is not realized
may little bit feel the cool breeze,

00:27:30.320 --> 00:27:32.640
may feel hot, you see,
the mixture of everything,

00:27:32.640 --> 00:27:35.840
so he’ll feel all the mixtures.

00:27:35.840 --> 00:27:39.120
Now you ask the lunatic
“From where do you come?”, they’ll say:

00:27:39.120 --> 00:27:42.800
“We are certified mad
coming from lunatic asylum”.

00:27:42.800 --> 00:27:47.440
You ask the patient, he’ll say that
“I’m from such and such place”.

00:27:47.440 --> 00:27:55.120
But people do not want to see this fact.
Is very simple to verify.

00:27:55.120 --> 00:28:00.320
Now moreover, the credibility of a person
who is taking money from you,

00:28:00.320 --> 00:28:04.320
taking everything from you,
is putting you on the street,

00:28:04.320 --> 00:28:10.480
who is making other people mad,
has to be challenged.

00:28:10.480 --> 00:28:16.480
Instead of that they will challenge My
credibility, but not of those people –

00:28:16.480 --> 00:28:21.680
the reason is you are no more there,
you are hypnotized, you will not.

00:28:21.680 --> 00:28:25.600
But here you are free,
and you should challenge.

00:28:25.600 --> 00:28:31.840
I appreciate it because of freedom,
is an expression, you are free to challenge.

00:28:31.840 --> 00:28:38.800
But that doesn’t mean freedom is a license
to again drift into nonsense.

00:28:38.800 --> 00:28:43.360
You keep your mind open,
receive your realization.

00:28:44.240 --> 00:28:52.560
I do not know in what words to say
that you are the ones who have been

00:28:52.560 --> 00:28:56.320
seeking truth for ages now.

00:28:56.320 --> 00:29:01.840
In the mountains, in the hills,
in the dales, in the Himalayas,

00:29:01.840 --> 00:29:06.320
and all over you have been seeking
for thousands and thousands of years.

00:29:06.320 --> 00:29:12.720
You are seekers, you are a special
category of people, and you must seek it,

00:29:12.720 --> 00:29:18.560
you must find it, instead of it
you seek your hell.

00:29:18.560 --> 00:29:24.480
What can a person like Me feel about it?
Is such a tragic thing,

00:29:24.480 --> 00:29:30.480
that the one who is really seeking
the reality is lost.

00:29:30.480 --> 00:29:39.520
I wish you could understand My concern
and My anguish, that: look at these people,

00:29:39.520 --> 00:29:45.760
they have been seeking, seeking God,
they are such nice people, such good people

00:29:45.760 --> 00:29:56.240
– are being harmed, have been tortured,
are now on their way to hell.

00:29:56.240 --> 00:30:03.040
It’s a very, very sad situation,
and that I am trying My level best

00:30:03.040 --> 00:30:07.440
to convince you that you seek the truth.

00:30:07.440 --> 00:30:09.440
You ask for the truth.

00:30:09.440 --> 00:30:15.120
And you get it, establish it,
and save others who are being ruined.

00:30:15.120 --> 00:30:19.200
Because they will be seeking in any case
whatever you may try,

00:30:19.200 --> 00:30:22.560
till the end they will be seeking,
till they are drowned completely.

00:30:22.560 --> 00:30:25.840
They are seekers.

00:30:25.840 --> 00:30:29.040
Today we were coming and one
of the sahaja yogini was sitting

00:30:29.040 --> 00:30:31.680
at the back in the airplane.

00:30:31.680 --> 00:30:35.760
And there was a fellow sitting next to her
who was reading some book on meditation.

00:30:35.760 --> 00:30:38.000
And she, she asked him,
‘Are you a seeker?’.

00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:39.040
He said: ‘Yes, I am’.

00:30:39.040 --> 00:30:43.680
And he got his realization
in the airplane.

00:30:43.680 --> 00:30:48.320
She herself has come to Me I think,
about few months back.

00:30:48.320 --> 00:30:51.600
And she gave him realization
and he got his realization.

00:30:52.400 --> 00:30:56.240
You could see from his eyes,
absolutely sparkling eyes he had.

00:30:56.240 --> 00:30:59.040
You could see he could feel the vibrations
and the cool breeze.

00:30:59.040 --> 00:31:05.040
And then you learn further steps
how to organize it, how to maneuver it,

00:31:05.040 --> 00:31:06.320
how to manage it.

00:31:06.320 --> 00:31:10.240
So you have to be connected
with the mains.

00:31:10.240 --> 00:31:12.480
You have to become divine.

00:31:12.480 --> 00:31:18.000
Not that you are not, you are;
but you are not aware of it.

00:31:18.000 --> 00:31:24.000
It is not in your conscious awareness,
it is not in your central nervous system.

00:31:24.000 --> 00:31:29.600
Whatever is in our central nervous system
is our achievement in our evolution.

00:31:29.600 --> 00:31:34.640
And you have to attain a little more step
and you become that.

00:31:34.640 --> 00:31:39.360
Like a triggering into the space
has to take place.

00:31:39.360 --> 00:31:46.000
This has to happen, and this will happen,
that thousands of you are to be saved.

00:31:46.000 --> 00:31:51.680
In some countries it has worked wonders,
especially in a country like Australia,

00:31:51.680 --> 00:31:57.911
imagine. You had banished them, sent them
away as criminals or whatever they were –

00:31:57.911 --> 00:32:00.640
they had children, their grandchildren,
and their great-grandchildren

00:32:00.640 --> 00:32:02.400
are great sahaja yogis.

00:32:02.400 --> 00:32:08.240
It’s spreading like fire,
the media is so sensitive, so sensible.

00:32:08.240 --> 00:32:14.800
While here I find there is no movement
in a country where I accepted,

00:32:14.800 --> 00:32:20.400
and expected that it could be
a tremendous thing.

00:32:20.960 --> 00:32:26.160
Let’s see, let’s see, still I leave it
to you people to find out ways

00:32:26.160 --> 00:32:31.600
and methods of cracking the brains here.

00:32:31.600 --> 00:32:34.920
Of course England was very difficult too,
for four years I was struggling

00:32:34.920 --> 00:32:37.680
with seven people, no doubt.

00:32:37.680 --> 00:32:44.480
But English, once they are cracked,
they are very wise.

00:32:44.480 --> 00:32:50.800
And somehow or other
these seven people proved it so well,

00:32:50.800 --> 00:32:54.240
and they found the change
because they were drug addicts,

00:32:54.240 --> 00:33:00.560
they had lots of troubles, and they were
about to collapse, some of them were

00:33:00.560 --> 00:33:04.400
absolutely in a coma when they came to Me,
so the change, the tremendous change

00:33:04.400 --> 00:33:07.280
in them convinced other people.

00:33:07.280 --> 00:33:11.280
And today we have very good
thousand sahaja yogis at least,

00:33:11.280 --> 00:33:15.840
very good thousand sahaja yogis
who are experts, who are masters

00:33:15.840 --> 00:33:22.800
in Kundalini Yoga in England.

00:33:22.800 --> 00:33:26.800
Now, as they have told you about all
these centers and all these things,

00:33:26.800 --> 00:33:30.800
today I would like to give a little
introduction about it,

00:33:30.800 --> 00:33:35.920
but later on I will tell you
how the key developments

00:33:35.920 --> 00:33:40.720
in the human awareness started
and how later on the whole thing

00:33:40.720 --> 00:33:42.080
was revealed.

00:33:42.080 --> 00:33:50.800
And today is the time when one can
talk about it so openly.

00:33:50.800 --> 00:33:54.400
I think you have given them the names
and everything of the chakras.

00:33:56.080 --> 00:33:59.840
But even knowing all about it,
is of no help.

00:33:59.840 --> 00:34:03.760
You must get your realization,
only knowing about them in a bookish way

00:34:03.760 --> 00:34:05.520
is of no use.

00:34:05.520 --> 00:34:10.400
You must get your realization,
that is very important.

00:34:10.400 --> 00:34:14.720
In India very few people really bother
about these things,

00:34:14.720 --> 00:34:19.920
because they know Kundalini awakening
is the only way, like sprouting of a seed.

00:34:19.920 --> 00:34:22.960
They know that Mother is the one
who is going to do it, second point,

00:34:22.960 --> 00:34:26.240
because Adi Shankaracharya has seen
and this and that.

00:34:26.240 --> 00:34:30.080
Third point they know that once
you get your realization

00:34:30.080 --> 00:34:34.640
you become the Brahmin or the one
who knows the Brahma.

00:34:34.640 --> 00:34:36.800
So in a village I have no problem.

00:34:36.800 --> 00:34:39.600
Thousands of people, if they come
to know that Mother is coming,

00:34:39.600 --> 00:34:42.000
there could be six thousand people
in a village.

00:34:42.000 --> 00:34:46.000
All will gather from all over
and they will get their realization

00:34:46.000 --> 00:34:53.360
so quick, I mean, so fast,
just like an American fast jet.

00:34:53.360 --> 00:34:55.280
Real fast they do it.

00:34:55.280 --> 00:35:00.560
In such an American way,
that you can’t imagine that it’s like a jet.

00:35:00.560 --> 00:35:08.160
And all of them getting, and such a wave
of beautiful Chatanya Lahari,

00:35:08.160 --> 00:35:15.440
these vibrations, cool breeze blowing,
just like the waves of the sea or an ocean,

00:35:15.440 --> 00:35:18.720
it’s beautiful to see that many.

00:35:18.720 --> 00:35:22.800
I mean, coming to America
some Indians were criticizing:

00:35:22.800 --> 00:35:27.120
“Why should You go to America?
Why not do it here?

00:35:27.120 --> 00:35:30.560
In one day You give realization
to six thousand people.

00:35:30.560 --> 00:35:34.560
There one day You might get one
and he’ll also slip out”.

00:35:34.560 --> 00:35:37.520
And they were criticizing My coming
to America.

00:35:37.520 --> 00:35:41.520
That not in a bad way, but in a good way,
that “It’s better that You spend

00:35:41.520 --> 00:35:44.320
Your time in India”.

00:35:44.320 --> 00:35:47.840
But here are the real seekers.

00:35:47.840 --> 00:35:51.280
They get it in India
because they are too simple;

00:35:51.280 --> 00:35:54.880
they are so innocent.
They have no problems.

00:35:54.880 --> 00:36:03.280
Here are the real seekers who are like,
we can say, the people in a war front,

00:36:03.280 --> 00:36:08.640
who do espionage, or something like that,
a very serious type of work,

00:36:08.640 --> 00:36:13.760
get complicated, get involved,
caught up by the enemies,

00:36:13.760 --> 00:36:18.560
and tortured by the enemies,
which are so dearer.

00:36:18.560 --> 00:36:22.240
Those are the heroes,
and they must be saved.

00:36:22.240 --> 00:36:24.160
That’s how I am here.

00:36:24.160 --> 00:36:30.320
And I know that once Americans take it up
we can save the whole world.

00:36:30.320 --> 00:36:33.680
It’s very simple to understand.

00:36:33.680 --> 00:36:40.240
But the way so far you have been
taking up to people is so amazingly foolish

00:36:40.240 --> 00:36:43.600
that people think that you
would never take to Me,

00:36:43.600 --> 00:36:47.520
because I am too sane,
I am too sensible,

00:36:47.520 --> 00:36:54.560
and they still are very diffident
about My work in New York especially.

00:36:54.560 --> 00:36:58.400
But to see you all here today,
I am overjoyed.

00:36:58.400 --> 00:37:02.400
I have great faith in you, you have
no idea how much faith I have.

00:37:02.400 --> 00:37:11.920
You are born in that special chakra,
which is the chakra of Shri Krishna.

00:37:11.920 --> 00:37:17.040
Is the chakra of the Primordial Being,
is the chakra from where

00:37:17.040 --> 00:37:20.000
the collectivity is first.

