Then, on the right side, when we talk big,
egoistical, when we try to push down people,

00:37:51.280 --> 00:37:56.080
specially when we try to dominate,
say within husband and wife,

00:37:56.080 --> 00:37:59.600
which we see all the time if there’s
a quarrel going on,

00:37:59.600 --> 00:38:03.600
your chakra will be ruined completely
on the right side.

00:38:03.600 --> 00:38:07.360
Left side is another problem
that comes from feeling guilty.

00:38:07.360 --> 00:38:10.560
And which is also very common.

00:38:10.560 --> 00:38:15.760
So these three centers that are the most
important thing and the most powerful

00:38:15.760 --> 00:38:20.080
in you people here, see how this is
attacked.

00:38:20.640 --> 00:38:27.040
Moreover the mantras and all that
which are not awakened by a realized soul,

00:38:27.040 --> 00:38:32.240
by a holy person,
can also ruin your left…

00:38:32.240 --> 00:38:36.800
Is very common with the people
who have done mantras, and chakra,

00:38:36.800 --> 00:38:39.760
and all of those things
without any authority.

00:38:39.760 --> 00:38:45.840
Because the whole thing comes up here,
just, and when you take the responsibility

00:38:45.840 --> 00:38:52.400
of such things on your back, say you take
on your shoulders the responsibility

00:38:52.400 --> 00:38:57.840
of wrong type of people, you can imagine,
what would be the shape and condition

00:38:57.840 --> 00:39:03.920
of that wonderful center which was created
in a human being when he raised his head

00:39:03.920 --> 00:39:06.240
from animal stage to look forward.

00:39:06.240 --> 00:39:11.040
Is a special thing that happened to us
when we raised our head like that,

00:39:11.040 --> 00:39:17.040
that within us these two centers,
these two things like, ego and superego,

00:39:17.040 --> 00:39:18.400
started developing.

00:39:18.400 --> 00:39:22.080
We had superego alright,
but the ego started developing

00:39:22.080 --> 00:39:26.640
when we just raised our head from
animal stage to this stage.

00:39:26.640 --> 00:39:31.920
But we do not know that if you raise
your head too much backwards like this,

00:39:31.920 --> 00:39:36.640
it can be spoilt. That means the ego
goes too much … then your head

00:39:36.640 --> 00:39:37.280
goes down like that.

00:39:37.280 --> 00:39:39.440
Such people never put down their heads
you see.

00:39:39.440 --> 00:39:43.760
If you see somebody walking like this,
find out: he must be something big

00:39:43.760 --> 00:39:47.200
somewhere, or aware that he is a very
big man.

00:39:47.840 --> 00:39:55.200
So the center that is the Vishuddhi
chakra is this America.

00:39:55.200 --> 00:40:01.440
And you are the people who are the cells
of that chakra which can be awakened.

00:40:01.440 --> 00:40:05.040
You are the cells and you are
to be awakened.

00:40:05.040 --> 00:40:09.600
Once you are awakened you can cure
this center and the whole universe

00:40:09.600 --> 00:40:11.520
will be benefited by that.

00:40:11.520 --> 00:40:16.000
That’s why I request you to understand
your position in the whole cosmos,

00:40:16.000 --> 00:40:21.280
of the universe, and the important
and the pivotal position that you have,

00:40:21.280 --> 00:40:26.800
and the wider role that you have to play,
so that you pay attention to yourself,

00:40:26.800 --> 00:40:33.280
your development, your growth,
and you achieve your full maturity

00:40:33.280 --> 00:40:34.960
in Sahaja Yoga.

00:40:34.960 --> 00:40:36.240
May God bless you all.

00:40:36.240 --> 00:40:43.280
I would like to have some questions today,
and then after that we can have

00:40:43.280 --> 00:40:59.680
the realization. Can you open the window?

00:41:14.000 --> 00:41:18.080
Yes. Tomorrow, as he is saying that
many of them have had no idea

00:41:18.080 --> 00:41:20.560
about the chakras and all that,
because they have come

00:41:20.560 --> 00:41:21.920
for the first time today,

00:41:21.920 --> 00:41:25.200
but tomorrow I am going to tell you
all about chakras and all that.

00:41:25.200 --> 00:41:27.840
Everything I’ll go gradually
one by one.

00:41:27.840 --> 00:41:32.160
Now I’ll be here for five lectures,
and I will see that in every lecture

00:41:32.160 --> 00:41:37.840
I’ll try to do step-by-step,
across the thing. And I will explain you.

00:41:42.400 --> 00:41:46.480
And also put them somewhere
for advertising.

00:41:46.480 --> 00:41:49.440
And moreover there is a book,
you can read that,

00:41:49.440 --> 00:41:52.400
but do not try to remember everything
by heart.

00:41:53.040 --> 00:41:56.480
It will be all your own,
the whole knowledge will be your own,

00:41:56.480 --> 00:42:00.000
it won’t be difficult.
So it’s not to be studied,

00:42:00.000 --> 00:42:03.040
but it’s to be felt.

00:42:03.040 --> 00:42:07.120
I will definitely tell you all about
chakras, and I’ll make you masters.

00:42:07.120 --> 00:42:11.360
I’m going to make you gurus,
every one of them. Real gurus.

00:42:11.360 --> 00:42:14.880
There’s one fellow in India,
who’s got his realization,

00:42:14.880 --> 00:42:18.160
and he’s given realization to,
as far as I know, ten thousand –

00:42:18.160 --> 00:42:21.907
but some people, twenty thousand –
they say they are twenty thousand people

00:42:21.907 --> 00:42:26.160
he has given realization.
So it’s possible.

00:42:26.160 --> 00:42:28.160
Yes, please?

00:42:28.160 --> 00:42:32.880
Mother, I do not mean to be funny,
but I felt a cool breeze

00:42:32.880 --> 00:42:34.320
for quite some time.

00:42:34.320 --> 00:42:37.120
You are not funny! You are very good,
you have got it!

00:42:37.120 --> 00:42:40.800
But I cannot tell that
whether it was the wind! (Laughter)

00:42:40.800 --> 00:42:45.520
It happens with everyone, because
we’ve opened it just now, alright?

00:42:48.880 --> 00:42:51.680
There is no wind here,
you can see that nothing is moving.

00:42:52.640 --> 00:42:58.240
Otherwise these things will be moving.
Yes, it’s alright, you got it very well.

00:42:59.200 --> 00:43:02.480
That is a thing I knew
you are going to get it. Alright?

00:43:02.480 --> 00:43:05.920
So nothing to be funny,
is the absolute truth.

00:43:05.920 --> 00:43:09.760
There was a scientist we had,
he was from Orissa.

00:43:09.760 --> 00:43:14.160
And he got his realization.
Then he looked at all the windows,

00:43:14.160 --> 00:43:15.680
and I was just smiling.

00:43:15.680 --> 00:43:18.396
Then he looked at his…
he turned like this,

00:43:18.396 --> 00:43:21.360
and then he had more from Me,
he couldn’t believe it.

00:43:21.360 --> 00:43:26.320
Then he went home,
he shut himself in a cellar,

00:43:26.320 --> 00:43:29.360
there he put, what you call, a candle.

00:43:29.360 --> 00:43:32.240
And then he put his hands to the candle
and the candle started giving him

00:43:32.240 --> 00:43:33.040
cool breeze!

00:43:33.040 --> 00:43:36.400
He couldn’t believe it, he thought
there’s something gone wrong with him.

00:43:36.400 --> 00:43:39.920
And now today he is
a very great sahaja yogi. Alright?

00:43:39.920 --> 00:43:43.280
So the first step has started,
that proves one thing beyond doubt,

00:43:43.280 --> 00:43:49.520
that you are a great seeker. Alright?
My congratulations.

00:43:49.520 --> 00:44:05.280
He has feelings for his family
and friends,

00:44:05.280 --> 00:44:09.160
but he has been seeking
for a love relationship with a woman

00:44:09.160 --> 00:44:09.514
without any success,

00:44:09.514 --> 00:44:21.760
which is causing him a lot of pain,
and he does not know what to do.

00:44:22.560 --> 00:44:24.480
See, I’ll tell you what happens.

00:44:24.480 --> 00:44:27.920
You have got a center here
is of the Nabhi, alright?

00:44:27.920 --> 00:44:30.800
Now out of this, is the left Nabhi here.

00:44:30.800 --> 00:44:36.960
If it is in a problem, left Nabhi
is the center of Gruha Lakshmi.

00:44:36.960 --> 00:44:42.320
Is the center of the Goddess
in the household, or your wife, see.

00:44:42.320 --> 00:44:47.360
Of course these days you don’t find
Goddesses as wives, but still! (Laughter)

00:44:47.360 --> 00:44:52.240
So, if that goes out, you see,
then lots of problems also can come up,

00:44:52.240 --> 00:44:55.760
but one of them is
that you get such a situation.

00:44:55.760 --> 00:45:01.680
But all such situations can be overcome,
all kinds of situations:

00:45:01.680 --> 00:45:06.560
people who have had perverted
relationships also get sorted out,

00:45:06.560 --> 00:45:14.480
those who have had, what you call,
the problems of divorce

00:45:14.480 --> 00:45:19.920
and sort of a relationship with a woman
and they are frightened of women,

00:45:19.920 --> 00:45:24.400
or the women who are dominating
or they don’t know how to stop their

00:45:24.400 --> 00:45:28.400
domination – they don’t want to dominate
but they somehow dominate –

00:45:28.400 --> 00:45:31.360
all these things will be sorted out.
No problem.

00:45:31.360 --> 00:45:34.640
Next year you will be married
very nicely. Alright?

00:45:34.640 --> 00:45:38.720
We had sixteen marriages
(laughter, Shri Mataji laughs)

00:45:38.720 --> 00:45:40.640
recently in England.

00:45:41.200 --> 00:45:43.760
One of them was Warren, who was married.

00:45:43.760 --> 00:45:49.120
And he is a divorcee, and he had given up
hopes of marriage.

00:45:49.120 --> 00:45:54.560
We had sixteen marriages
the day of Krishna’s birthday.

00:45:54.560 --> 00:45:56.240
So don’t you worry.

00:45:56.240 --> 00:46:01.040
But you have to follow
certain understanding of maintaining

00:46:01.040 --> 00:46:06.080
yourself in a position, see,
and I’ll tell you all about it,

00:46:06.080 --> 00:46:07.200
how to do it.

00:46:07.200 --> 00:46:12.960
And you will have very good marriages,
lasting marriages, not only that;

00:46:12.960 --> 00:46:16.320
but you’ll have realized souls
as your children.

00:46:16.320 --> 00:46:18.480
There are many who want to be born.

00:46:18.480 --> 00:46:25.280
And all the sahaja yogis who are married
now have got realized souls as children.

00:46:25.280 --> 00:46:32.000
Because they want to be born,
they want parents who understand them,

00:46:32.000 --> 00:46:35.840
who can bear them, who can look after them,
and love them.

00:46:35.840 --> 00:46:39.120
So you will have everything fine,
don’t you worry.

00:46:39.120 --> 00:46:48.320
And a very nice wife too. Alright? Yes?

00:46:53.600 --> 00:46:58.240
There are subconscious impurities.

00:46:59.760 --> 00:47:02.960
I am happy that you have reached
the right conclusion.

00:47:02.960 --> 00:47:05.120
Don’t you worry, I know how
to look after them.

00:47:05.120 --> 00:47:06.160
That’s all I’ll say.

00:47:06.160 --> 00:47:09.040
And I will teach you how to do it
for others also.

00:47:09.040 --> 00:47:12.800
You will become Saint Michael
in this respect. Alright?

00:47:12.800 --> 00:47:16.640
And we’ll have to drive them out,
all the subconscious impurities.

00:47:16.640 --> 00:47:22.560
I think we have got our book here,
of the Advent.

00:47:22.560 --> 00:47:29.200
Alright. In that it is, see, Gregoire,
the one who has written the book,

00:47:29.200 --> 00:47:33.200
has called them as UPI, I don’t know
what it means (laughs) but he calls them

00:47:33.200 --> 00:47:37.760
as UPI, and there are so many methods
by which we can drive them out. Eh?

00:47:37.760 --> 00:47:44.505
What is it?
Units of Psychic Interference.

00:47:44.505 --> 00:47:47.280
Ah ok! (Shri Mataji laughs)
That’s all the invention. Don’t worry.

00:47:47.280 --> 00:47:51.120
You just don’t worry.
Not only yours, but others, you know.

00:47:51.120 --> 00:47:55.360
When you will go on the road, if they
know that you are passing that way,

00:47:55.360 --> 00:47:58.160
they’ll all disappear.
You become so powerful.

00:48:00.880 --> 00:48:03.200
Now will you forget them?

00:48:03.200 --> 00:48:08.640
Forget it, forget your past.
Forget it, that is subconscious,

00:48:08.640 --> 00:48:10.240
just forget it.

00:48:10.240 --> 00:48:15.120
Do you know that all the sins
and blasphemy is to be forgiven,

00:48:15.120 --> 00:48:19.920
and it’s been already promised?
Because you are saints!

00:48:21.440 --> 00:48:24.240
So don’t count them at all, forget it.

00:48:24.240 --> 00:48:28.480
You see, when you wash the clothes,
say in a washing machine,

00:48:28.480 --> 00:48:32.520
will you count all the stains?
It’s like that.

00:48:32.520 --> 00:48:36.640
Kundalini washes you up
and cleanses you completely.

00:48:36.640 --> 00:48:40.160
It’s your own Kundalini, it is pure,
holy, your own Mother.

00:48:40.160 --> 00:48:45.960
She’ll wash it up, don’t you worry.
Alright?

00:48:45.960 --> 00:48:46.800
Yes.

00:48:46.800 --> 00:48:50.080
It’s too much to believe, is it?
(Laughs, laughter) it is so.

00:48:50.080 --> 00:48:57.120
Because you don’t know what you are,
you are fantastic.

00:48:57.120 --> 00:49:02.720
What worries you? What is worrying you?

00:49:15.360 --> 00:49:18.000
She thinks she has taken somebody
into her house who is not good,

00:49:18.000 --> 00:49:21.680
and she thinks she is becoming
not good as a result of that.

00:49:21.680 --> 00:49:25.360
See, there are solutions
for that kind of thing.

00:49:25.360 --> 00:49:30.320
If he is really a sinister fellow,
he’ll run away. Alright.

00:49:30.320 --> 00:49:35.200
Or in case he is capable of improvement,
he’ll improve.

00:49:35.200 --> 00:49:38.907
So you become more powerful than them.
You see?

00:49:38.907 --> 00:49:42.960
Is what is more powerful is the point.

00:49:42.960 --> 00:49:50.320
If the light is more powerful,
the darkness has to run away. Alright?

00:49:50.320 --> 00:49:55.680
So because you still do not know
your powers, and to maneuver it,

00:49:55.680 --> 00:49:59.200
that’s why you are worrying.
But once you know it’s very simple.

00:49:59.200 --> 00:50:04.080
Once you are realized I will tell you
how to use it, and you’ll be amazed.

00:50:04.080 --> 00:50:07.200
Like yesterday I was coming,
and suddenly I had to go,

00:50:07.200 --> 00:50:11.600
and there was no seat available
in the plane, and so my husband told Me,

00:50:11.600 --> 00:50:14.160
“I’m sorry, there’s no seat
available for you”,

00:50:14.160 --> 00:50:16.400
and suddenly he said: “Oh, it’s
a miraculous thing, they have said

00:50:16.400 --> 00:50:18.720
there’s some seat”.
I said: “Alright, book Me there”.

00:50:18.720 --> 00:50:20.160
And two others were coming with me.

00:50:20.160 --> 00:50:25.120
– See, this is absolutely a material life,
absolutely a material level, isn’t it? –

00:50:25.120 --> 00:50:29.280
And two others were coming,
there was no seat at any cost.

00:50:29.280 --> 00:50:33.280
And two people who had booked
for one month before, ahead, dropped out

00:50:33.280 --> 00:50:36.320
and these two were with Me
in the airplane.

00:50:36.320 --> 00:50:41.120
So even at a very, very material level
they help you.

00:50:41.120 --> 00:50:45.280
And spiritual level I need not tell you.

00:50:45.280 --> 00:50:47.920
Even at the very baser material level
they help you,

00:50:47.920 --> 00:50:53.588
because this Lakshmi tattwa is here
which helps you for the well-being.

00:50:53.588 --> 00:50:56.080
Krishna has said:
Yogakshema Vahamyam,

00:50:56.080 --> 00:50:59.360
I’ll look after your Yoga first,
Yoga means the union,

00:50:59.360 --> 00:51:05.360
first you must get your union,
and then the well-being, Kshema.

00:51:05.360 --> 00:51:10.160
In America we have got the Kshema first,
the well-being, the Yoga is missing.

00:51:15.120 --> 00:51:16.240
(She smiles, laughter)

00:51:16.240 --> 00:51:18.080
I wanted to ask a question to Mother.

00:51:18.080 --> 00:51:18.720
Yes, please.

00:51:18.720 --> 00:51:20.120
First I would like to say that
You were an inspiration…

00:51:20.120 --> 00:51:24.720
What is it?
You are an inspiration to him, Mother.

00:51:24.720 --> 00:51:27.680
Ah?
You are an inspiration to him.

00:51:27.680 --> 00:51:30.160
Oh, I see. May God bless you.

00:51:30.160 --> 00:51:33.360
I am sure all of us have hundreds
of questions that would keep You here

00:51:33.360 --> 00:51:37.120
the whole night, but I would like to say
that I would like to become

00:51:37.120 --> 00:51:40.880
a realized being and give the answers
from within.

00:51:40.880 --> 00:51:47.360
So my question is: after the five
lectures, and You leave us,

00:51:47.360 --> 00:51:48.800
where do we go from there?

00:51:49.440 --> 00:51:53.200
I know, everybody feels sad (laughter).

00:51:53.200 --> 00:51:57.680
Because you are like small children,
you know. But you grow so fast.

00:51:57.680 --> 00:52:05.680
That you are amazed, you see. You grow.
You grow very fast. You’ll all grow.

00:52:05.680 --> 00:52:08.080
I’m not going to leave you.

00:52:08.080 --> 00:52:12.480
I’m going to come back again and again,
and you are all going to come to India,

00:52:12.480 --> 00:52:21.600
and we are all going to have
a very nice time (laughter).

00:52:21.600 --> 00:52:34.720
We all belong to each other:
how can we leave you? Now.

00:52:34.720 --> 00:52:38.000
Is it alright, or any other question?

00:52:38.000 --> 00:52:42.080
Even if you have any personal questions
or anything you can write to Me, alright?

00:52:42.080 --> 00:52:44.320
If you don’t want to discuss it here.

00:52:44.320 --> 00:52:53.520
And tomorrow morning if they can come
to the hotel – at the hotel you can come,

00:52:53.520 --> 00:52:59.259
I can work it out for you if you have
any personal problems or anything,

00:52:59.259 --> 00:52:59.600
we’ll work it out, alright?

00:52:59.600 --> 00:53:11.600
I’m here for a complete 24-hours
in the hotel.

00:53:12.960 --> 00:53:16.960
You can ask a question
and you get the answer.

00:53:19.840 --> 00:53:23.640
Yes.
And how do you read that, how do you know…

00:53:23.640 --> 00:53:30.320
See, what happens, now say for example
you are connected to a mains. Alright?

00:53:30.320 --> 00:53:35.120
Now the mains is an unconsciousness
was so far, it has become a consciousness

00:53:35.120 --> 00:53:39.440
within you. You are like a computer
I would say, to make things easy.

00:53:39.440 --> 00:53:40.960
It’s a mystery again.

00:53:40.960 --> 00:53:45.040
So you put your hands
and ask a question: “Mother, is there God?”.

00:53:45.040 --> 00:53:49.200
Just see vibrations. Right?
“Mother, is there God?”.

00:53:49.200 --> 00:53:53.200
And three times if you ask,
you get tremendous vibrations,

00:53:53.200 --> 00:53:58.069
already must have started. You see, so,
that’s how you will know.

00:53:58.069 --> 00:54:02.720
But if you ask about somebody
who is not a real guru,

00:54:02.720 --> 00:54:07.200
who is not a real person,
then you might even get burning.

00:54:07.200 --> 00:54:13.040
Sometimes you might even get blisters.
You may lose your vibrations.

00:54:13.040 --> 00:54:15.520
The more you grow
the more you become sensitive,

00:54:15.520 --> 00:54:18.400
and you start understanding where you are.

00:54:18.400 --> 00:54:21.520
Can you also ask practical questions
about your life?

00:54:21.520 --> 00:54:27.040
Yes, yes, you will. In the beginning
everybody asks: should I buy this?

00:54:27.040 --> 00:54:30.480
Or that? (Laughter, Shri Mataji laughs).
Then the questions start becoming

00:54:30.480 --> 00:54:34.240
subtler and subtler,
because your priorities change.

00:54:34.240 --> 00:54:38.080
Whatever level you are,
you start asking questions.

00:54:38.080 --> 00:54:41.200
Then no questions, at a stage
which we call…

00:54:41.200 --> 00:54:46.320
first you get thoughtless awareness,
as your… first you get thoughtless awareness.

00:54:46.320 --> 00:54:49.920
In Sanskrit, it is called
as “nirvichar samadhi”.

00:54:49.920 --> 00:54:58.640
Sama-dhi: “Dhi” means your consciousness,
and sama-dhi is the one which is enlightened.

00:54:58.640 --> 00:55:03.360
So, the thoughtless enlightened
awareness first.

00:55:03.360 --> 00:55:09.200
Then the second state is –
which you have to establish –

00:55:09.200 --> 00:55:14.400
is called as Nirvikalpa samadhi,
meaning doubtless awareness.

00:55:14.400 --> 00:55:17.600
It is a state; it is not:
“I have no doubts about Mother,

00:55:17.600 --> 00:55:20.800
I have no doubts about Sahaja Yoga”,
is not that.

00:55:20.800 --> 00:55:25.760
And that state is achieved, and at both
the states when you are say

00:55:25.760 --> 00:55:33.440
thoughtlessly aware state, you can give
awakening, you can give realization,

00:55:33.440 --> 00:55:37.600
you can cure cancer, you can cure
all kinds of diseases,

00:55:37.600 --> 00:55:41.200
so many things you can do
with the first shot.

00:55:41.200 --> 00:55:44.080
But much do not indulge in that too much.

00:55:44.080 --> 00:55:49.680
You can give realization at the most,
and then you should jump onto the second stage

00:55:49.680 --> 00:55:52.000
where you become Nirvikalpa.

00:55:52.000 --> 00:56:00.000
Means where you are doubtlessly aware.
Doubtlessly enlightened awareness.

